name: General Tagge (V)
Lore: 'Oversees defense operations of Death Star. Outstanding tactician. No-nonsense leader. Member of the House of Tagge, a powerful noble family and corporate conglomerate.',
Text: 'During your control phase, may use 1 Force to take an Imperial trooper without armor into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per game, may place all your non-[Immune to Alter] Effects in Used Pile.',
